### Login (replace creds)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "adminpass"
}

### Admin adjust stock
POST http://localhost:8000/api/admin/adjust-stock/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "technician_id": "{{tech1}}",
  "article_id": "{{article1}}",
  "operation": "add",
  "quantity": "5",
  "reason": "inventory_correction"
}

### Create reservation (as tech)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/reservations/create/
Authorization: Bearer {{tech_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "technician_id": "{{tech1}}",
  "article_id": "{{article1}}",
  "qty_reserved": "2"
}

### Approve reservation
POST http://localhost:8000/api/reservations/{{reservation_id}}/approve/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Transfer
POST http://localhost:8000/api/transfers/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from_technician_id": "{{tech1}}",
  "to_technician_id": "{{tech2}}",
  "article_id": "{{article1}}",
  "quantity": "1"
}


